## Filter cells

```{r filter}
merged_f <- subset(
  merged,
  subset = percent.mt < max_percent_mt &
    nFeature_RNA > min_nFeature &
    nFeature_RNA < max_nFeature
)

# Seurat v5 layers
merged_f <- JoinLayers(merged_f)

table(merged_f$orig.ident)
```

